text: Þis is þæt landgemere æt meresege þæt is ærest on pantan streame oð hit cymð to ðam dican betwyx east meresege and west <meresege>.
Ðonne of ðam dican into ðam fleote.
Ðonne of ðam fleote into ðære stræte þæt hit cymð to ðære petan.
Þonne on fingringaho <æt> ðam stane fram ðam stane to bricsfleotes orde æft fram ðam stane to Winnanbricse fram Winnanbricse to peltandunes meowte.
